h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Agent"|guide:ShowExhAgentActionService].
* Click the magnify icon from grid view.
* Write searching criteria.
* Press "Enter" button.
* Search *Agent* From Grid View.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "List Agent Company" privilege.
* Rules of Searching:
{table}
 *Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Searching Option*	
  Find | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | Name
{table}


h4. Process:
* Get list of *Agent* (default: 15 at Max) matching with search criteria.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** *Agent* will be listed in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

